{"id": 58369, "date": "2025-08-12T04:00:27", "date_gmt": "2025-08-12T11:00:27", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=58369"}, "modified": "2026-05-12T15:05:26", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-12T22:05:26", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-august-12-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/08/12/kingdom-of-days-august-12-2/", "title": {"rendered": "August 12"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1967:\u00a0</strong>The Castiles play the Surf &#8216;N&#8217;See Club in Sea Bright, New Jersey. That night, Bruce and some of his bandmates catch The Blues Magoos and The Who opening for Herman&#8217;s Hermits at Convention Hall in Asbury Park. Just a few weeks later, the band will cover The Blues Magoos&#8217; &#8220;One By One&#8221; in concert themselves.</p>\n<p><strong>1972:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays his fourth of six\u00a0two-shows-a-night solo gigs at Max&#8217;s Kansas City that week.</p>\n<p><strong>1974</strong>:\u00a0Bruce cancels a gig at the Cambridge Performance Center to make room for <em>Born to Run\u00a0</em>recording sessions.</p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Columbia Records begins distributing a limited run of advanced promo copies of\u00a0<em>Born to Run.</em></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3846\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1975-0812/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1975-0812.jpg?fit=872%2C631&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"872,631\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1975-0812\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1975-0812.jpg?fit=758%2C549&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3846 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1975-0812.jpg?resize=758%2C549&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"549\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1975-0812.jpg?w=872&amp;ssl=1 872w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1975-0812.jpg?resize=300%2C217&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1975-0812.jpg?resize=768%2C556&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>At Atlantic Studios in New York City, Bruce and the E Street Band record &#8220;Gotta Get That Feeling.&#8221; It will be released 38 years later.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/DQ1LfLDrDrU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLp97J3OSn7Isbkt20--RCkDWLCYDDJ3wX\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band bring the Darkness Tour to Augusta, Maine, for one show at the Civic Center.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3670\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-0812/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1978-0812.jpg?fit=666%2C885&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"666,885\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-0812\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1978-0812.jpg?fit=666%2C885&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3670 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1978-0812.jpg?resize=666%2C885&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"666\" height=\"885\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1978-0812.jpg?w=666&amp;ssl=1 666w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1978-0812.jpg?resize=226%2C300&amp;ssl=1 226w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 666px) 100vw, 666px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their second of two nights at Detroit&#8217;s Joe Louis Arena on the original River Tour. Mitch Ryder makes a guest appearance during the encores on (what else?) &#8220;Detroit Medley.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-O8YUTq5R-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/O8YUTq5R?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLJTyL9twk3zA1TFgf6jVO6s3jMFbLoHkt\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>Southside Johnny guest-stars on &#8220;Twist and Shout&#8221; at Night Six of a ten-night Meadowlands stand on the Born in the U.S.A. Tour.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xQWHgkEPO6M?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ltFmBMtLr3A?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1998:\u00a0</strong>Bruce takes in a Yankees game and stops by the clubhouse to sign a guitar.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/59rOfptTacI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20311\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1998-08-11a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11a.png?fit=1326%2C871&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1326,871\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1998-08-11a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11a.png?fit=758%2C498&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20311 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11a.png?resize=758%2C498&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"498\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11a.png?w=1326&amp;ssl=1 1326w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11a.png?resize=300%2C197&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11a.png?resize=1024%2C673&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11a.png?resize=768%2C504&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20312\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1998-08-11b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11b.png?fit=1373%2C1399&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1373,1399\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1998-08-11b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11b.png?fit=758%2C772&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20312 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11b.png?resize=758%2C772&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"772\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11b.png?w=1373&amp;ssl=1 1373w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11b.png?resize=294%2C300&amp;ssl=1 294w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11b.png?resize=1005%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1005w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11b.png?resize=768%2C783&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11b.png?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band wrap up their astounding fifteen-night Reunion stand at the Meadowlands with two long-awaited and inevitable bookends: the show-opening tour premiere of &#8220;Jersey Girl&#8221; and the show-closing one-off performance of &#8220;Rosalita (Come Out Tonight).&#8221; During the encores, Jon Bon Jovi, Richie Sambora, and Melissa Etheridge join Bruce and the band for &#8220;Hungry Heart.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/DNzLnlxJh20?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/tp5QXKa6DIU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div id=\"v-kGzGDIv0-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/kGzGDIv0?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20313\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1999-08-12/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-08-12.png?fit=1144%2C1404&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1144,1404\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1999-08-12\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-08-12.png?fit=758%2C931&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20313 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-08-12.png?resize=758%2C930&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"930\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-08-12.png?w=1144&amp;ssl=1 1144w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-08-12.png?resize=244%2C300&amp;ssl=1 244w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-08-12.png?resize=834%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 834w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-08-12.png?resize=768%2C943&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2002:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band bring the Rising Tour to Madison Square Garden, where they play the second of four identical set lists in one week. When the show ends, a new video of an acoustic arrangement of &#8220;Countin&#8217; on a Miracle&#8221; (directed by Danny Clinch) debuts.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/bFys3yQTPIc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div id=\"v-pNq9JhnV-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/pNq9JhnV?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-hUQAannx-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/hUQAannx?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"53991\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/newsday_2002_08_15_78/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Newsday_2002_08_15_78.jpg?fit=%2C&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"[]\" data-image-title=\"Newsday_2002_08_15_78\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Newsday_2002_08_15_78.jpg?fit=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-53991\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Newsday_2002_08_15_78.jpg?w=758&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>On this date: Mitch Ryder makes a &#8220;Detroit Medley&#8221; guest appearance, Bruce swings by the Yankees&#8217; clubhouse, the debut of the acoustic &#8220;Countin&#8217; on a Miracle&#8221; video, and more.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 11980, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false}, "categories": [2], "tags": [1433, 558, 1135, 508, 41, 610, 1228, 957, 173, 1434, 630, 549, 367, 376, 128, 291, 87], "class_list": ["post-58369", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-kingdom-of-days", "tag-augusta", "tag-born-in-the-usa-tour", "tag-countin-on-a-miracle", "tag-darkness-tour", "tag-detroit", "tag-east-rutherford", "tag-jersey-girl", "tag-madison-square-garden", "tag-maxs-kansas-city", "tag-mitch-ryder", "tag-new-york-city", "tag-out-in-the-street", "tag-reunion-tour", "tag-rising-tour", "tag-river-tour", "tag-rosalita", "tag-southside-johnny"], "aioseo_notices": [], "jetpack_publicize_connections": [], "jetpack_featured_media_url": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/19990812_2_front.jpg?fit=1076%2C928&ssl=1", "jetpack_sharing_enabled": true, "jetpack_shortlink": "https://wp.me/p9w3Lk-fbr", "jetpack_likes_enabled": true, "jetpack-related-posts": [{"id": 57795, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/22/kingdom-of-days-july-22-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 58369, "position": 0}, "title": "July 22", "author": "Ken", "date": "July 22, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "On this date: Bruce and Steve play an emotional tribute to the victims of the Norway attacks, Bruce makes surprise appearances with Southside Johnny and Joe Grushecky, and the feature documentary Springsteen & I is released to theaters worldwide.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bruce-springsteen.jpg?fit=1024%2C772&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bruce-springsteen.jpg?fit=1024%2C772&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bruce-springsteen.jpg?fit=1024%2C772&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bruce-springsteen.jpg?fit=1024%2C772&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x"}, "classes": []}, {"id